$ Documentation/admin-guide/cgroups-v2.rst

`Documentation/admin-guide/cgroups-v2.rst` contains the authoritative documentation of *cgroup v2* on the
  • design,
  • interface and
  • conventions

It also describes all userland-visible aspects of cgroup including core and specific controller behaviors.


Documentation for
v1 is available under :ref:`Documentation/admin-guide/cgroup-v1/index.rst <cgroup-v1>`.

sa:
 `Documentation/admin-guide/cgroup-v1/index.rst` contains the documentation for cgroup v1
